rticle/.premium/personal-safety-institutional-racism-the-challenges-facing-arab-israeli-mayors/0000018d-f51f-da4e-adbf-f7bff1b20000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对以色列的未来有一个愿景。内塔尼亚胡不</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-reckless-stupidity-in-ignoring-the-biden-plan-for-a-new-middle-east/0000018d-f41d-da4e-adbf-f6bdec4d0000</link><description>一个超级大国为一个规模小得多、不对称的盟友制定并提供长期大战略，就像美国总统乔·拜登正在制定的新中东计划一样，这是史无前例的。以色列至少能做的就是给予该计划应有的关注</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 13:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-reckless-stupidity-in-ignoring-the-biden-plan-for-a-new-middle-east/0000018d-f41d-da4e-adbf-f6bdec4d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>